<h3>The final examination consists of two tests:</h3>
<ul>
<li>the German language test for immigrants A2-B1 ( DTZ)</li>
<li>the orientation course test</li>
</ul>
<p>Taking the final test is free of charge. If you pass the language test at level B1 and the orientation course test, then you have passed the final examination. You will receive the "Zertifikat DTZ Deutschtest für Zuwanderer". If you pass the language test only at level A2, you are allowed to attend another 300 lessons.</p>
